article_title: Israel's border residents in fear of invasion from north
sentence: But  they  are  intense  and  deadly  -  nine  soldiers  and  four  civilians  have  been  killed  in  Israel,  officials  say,  while  authorities  in  Lebanon  have  reported  that  123  people  have  been  killed,  including  at  least  21  civilians.
